# Trivy ignore list — documented, deliberate exceptions ONLY. Each entry must have a
# justification. Keep this list short so genuinely new findings stand out.
#
# readOnlyRootFilesystem should be true (KSV0014 / AVD-KSV-0014).
# EXCEPTION (hermes-agent): the upstream image runs s6-overlay as PID 1, which writes
# to /run, so a read-only root filesystem breaks startup without extra scratch mounts.
# This is intentional and documented; a read-only-rootfs opt-in (with emptyDir scratch)
# is planned. See specs/04-security-model.md §4 and charts/hermes-agent/README.md.
AVD-KSV-0014
KSV-0014
KSV0014
